QuestData.Title: Jonesy Sent For You
QuestData.Description: Listen, $n, you may want to make your way back to Jonesy when you get a moment.$b$bChances are, whatever he's got to talk to you about is more pressing than anything I have for you to do.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Harrison Jones in the Oasis of Vir'sar.
QuestData.RewardText: Alright, kid.$b$bMy research is complete. We're about ready to activate the final obelisk.
